author: jukka
msg: TIKA-261: Ability to limit the amount of extracted text
Add a write limit feature to WriteOutContentHandler and use it in the Tika.parseToString() methods.
The write limit is set by default to 100k characters when buffering to memory, and disabled when streaming.
